				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "AD when interacting with the intellect devourer that is patrolling between the mindflayer room where a human is in a pod and can be transformed into an illithid and the room where two other thralls are in chairs and can be killed or turned hostile by pressing buttons.\r\n\r\nThe intellect devourer will recognize players as kin because of the tadpole, and without revealing too much mention how tadpoled people are being experimented on and turned into mindflayers."
				}
